:{{A|VO Side0 al asta 106.ogg}} '''Asta:''' It's been thirteen hours since he last contacted me. He usually takes less than 13 seconds to reply to my messages!
:{{A|VO Side0 al asta 107.ogg}} '''Asta:''' I looked everywhere and couldn't find him, so I checked the Security Department's work plan records. This is what I found!
:{{A|VO Side0 al asta 108.ogg}} '''Asta:''' Look, at his last work objectives entry: "Of the heart. Of the mirror. Of the self." It's so strange...
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} The entries for last week are pretty odd too.
::{{A|VO Side0 al asta 109.ogg}} '''Asta:''' ...Ahaha, d&mdash;don't worry about those.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Sure is.
