:{{DIcon|Arrow}} I think guys his age do tend to write like this.
::{{A|VO Side0 al asta 111.ogg}} '''Asta:''' ...B&mdash;But he's never written poetry before!
:{{A|VO Side0 al asta 112.ogg}} '''Asta:''' *sigh* I asked people in the Security Department, but none of them thought it was concerning. They said stuff like:
:{{A|VO Side0 al asta 113.ogg}} '''Asta:''' "Brother Arlan is a grown man with his own plans!"
:{{A|VO Side0 al asta 114.ogg}} '''Asta:''' I couldn't get them to listen at all, so I'm asking you for help.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} You don't have any clues, how can I&mdash;
::{{A|VO Side0 al asta 115.ogg}} '''Asta:''' I have a secret weapon! Say hello to...
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Guys his age just need "alone time" sometimes!
::{{A|VO Side0 al asta 116.ogg}} '''Asta:''' Why are you acting like those Security Department idiots!? Stop fooling around and help me!
::{{A|VO Side0 al asta 117.ogg}} '''Asta:''' I have a secret weapon! Say hello to...
:{{A|VO Side0 al asta 118.ogg}} '''Asta:''' Peppy!
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Peppy?
:{{A|VO Side0 al asta 119.ogg}} '''Asta:''' Mm-hmm, Peppy's my dog &mdash; Arlan's looked after him since he was a puppy. They're great friends.
:{{A|VO Side0 al asta 120.ogg}} '''Asta:''' Peppy knows Arlan's scent &mdash; maybe he can track him down.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Then... am I still needed?
::{{A|VO Side0 al asta 121.ogg}} '''Asta:''' Y&mdash;Yes! Think about it &mdash; if people see me, the acting lead researcher, searching for Arlan...
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Then get Peppy to find Arlan.
::{{A|VO Side0 al asta 122.ogg}} '''Asta:''' Peppy can't go alone. What if he gets lost too? And I can't go with him &mdash; if people see me, the acting lead researcher, searching for Arlan...
:{{A|VO Side0 al asta 123.ogg}} '''Asta:''' Wouldn't that... Wouldn't that make Arlan look incompetent as head of the Security Department?
:{{A|VO Side0 al asta 124.ogg}} '''Asta:''' ...Let's go together! Relax &mdash; Peppy doesn't bite.

