===Learn about Arlan's trial from Dan Heng{{subst:void|<!--200021116-->}}===
{{Mission Description|type=companion|location=Base Zone|update|The last of the Legion have been cleared out, and it's now safe to ask about Arlan's situation.<br />Ask Dan Heng about Arlan's trial and his current whereabouts.}}
