;(Obtain {{Item|Arlan's ID Pass|20|x=1}})

;(Talk to Dan Heng)
:{{A|VO Side0 al danheng 101.ogg}} '''Dan Heng:''' ...What are you doing here?
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} I'm here to protect a friend's secret.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} I'm here to find a lost friend.
:{{A|VO Side0 al danheng 102.ogg}} '''Dan Heng:''' ...Then be careful. There are still Legion remnants in the area.
:{{A|VO Side0 al danheng 103.ogg}} '''Dan Heng:''' Arlan isn't here right now, so we need to step up the space station's security. Spare no effort and stay focused.
:{{A|VO Side0 al staffAE 101.ogg}} '''Member of the Security Department:''' Yes, brother Dan Heng!
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} You saw Arlan?
::{{A|VO Side0 al danheng 104.ogg}} '''Dan Heng:''' Yes, he's with March.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Check you out, calling the shots...
::{{A|VO Side0 al danheng 105.ogg}} '''Dan Heng:''' *sigh* I'm only helping Arlan. You're here to look for him, right? He's with March.
:{{A|VO Side0 al danheng 106.ogg}} '''Dan Heng:''' But I suggest you don't bother him. He's given himself a personal trial.
:{{A|VO Side0 al staffAE 102.ogg}} '''Thrilled Member of the Security Department:''' Brother Arlan's special trial? He's a man among men, a lion among tigers! He's already reached great heights, but still he wants to improve!
:{{A|VO Side0 al staffAF 102.ogg}} '''Excited Member of the Security Department:''' That trial... I bet it's even more intense than physical training! And brother Arlan already challenges himself to the limit in that department &mdash; he runs 21,358 meters around the space station every day! An eagle among wolves! Always so hard on himself!
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} What kind of trial is it?
:{{A|VO Side0 al staffAE 103.ogg}} '''Thrilled Member of the Security Department:''' I think it must have something to do with the mind. He probably found a waterfall and asked Ms. March to lower the temperature to freezing point!
:{{A|VO Side0 al staffAF 103.ogg}} '''Excited Member of the Security Department:''' No way! Brother Arlan's trial wouldn't be as simple as just standing under a waterfall! I think he wants to learn fighting skills from Ms. March.
:{{A|VO Side0 al danheng 107.ogg}} '''Dan Heng:''' ...They're not correct, but not wrong either.
:{{A|VO Side0 al danheng 108.ogg}} '''Dan Heng:''' Arlan came to me to learn how to manage pressure from his boss.
:{{A|VO Side0 al danheng 109.ogg}} '''Dan Heng:''' ...So I sent him to March. If he can manage her, then he has nothing to fear.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} He's a bear among horses!
::{{A|VO Side0 al staffAE 104.ogg}} '''Thrilled Member of the Security Department:''' That might be a metaphor too far.
::{{A|VO Side0 al staffAF 104.ogg}} '''Excited Member of the Security Department:''' Brother Arlan runs like a horse and fights like a bear. I think that's a great metaphor!
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} That's pretty sadistic, Dan Heng.
::{{A|VO Side0 al staffAE 105.ogg}} '''Thrilled Member of the Security Department:''' I think brother Dan Heng is pretty smart.
::{{A|VO Side0 al staffAF 105.ogg}} '''Excited Member of the Security Department:''' Brother Arlan only has that one weakness in his armor, but he won't ignore it! He's too awesome for that!
:{{A|VO Side0 al danheng 110.ogg}} '''Dan Heng:''' ...Arlan and I decided to switch our assignments. He went with March to investigate a suspicious crystal, and I've taken up his patrol.
:{{A|VO Side0 al danheng 111.ogg}} '''Dan Heng:''' That's all.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Did Arlan leave anything with you?
:{{A|VO Side0 al danheng 118.ogg}} '''Dan Heng:''' He gave me a pass for access across the space station while on patrol.
