::{{A|VO Side0 al asta 214.ogg}} '''Asta:''' ...when I saw this photo, when I saw you fighting alone just now...
::{{A|VO Side0 al asta 215.ogg}} '''Asta:''' I'm just sorry that I gave you the stress of all my private affairs on top of an already stressful job.
::{{A|VO Side0 al asta 216.ogg}} '''Asta:''' Please forgive me, Arlan.
::{{A|VO Side0 al arlan 122.ogg}} '''Arlan:''' ...
::{{A|VO Side0 al arlan 123.ogg}} '''Arlan:''' My Lady, I... I'm very touched, but...
::{{A|VO Side0 al arlan 124.ogg}} '''Arlan:''' I started this trial because of Madam Herta.
::{{A|VO Side0 al mar7th 127.ogg}} '''March 7th and Asta:''' What!?
::{{A|VO Side0 al arlan 125.ogg}} '''Arlan:''' Whenever she's back on the space station, Madam Herta assigns me things outside the Security Department remit.
::{{A|VO Side0 al arlan 126.ogg}} '''Arlan:''' Even if I dared to refuse, I wouldn't know how. She's just... too overbearing.
::{{A|VO Side0 al arlan 127.ogg}} '''Arlan:''' Whether it's helping her test some new specimen, or looking for ancient documents I've never even heard of...
::{{A|VO Side0 al arlan 128.ogg}} '''Arlan:''' ...Assignments like those were okay before the invasion, but now I need to focus on clearing out any last traces of the Legion.
::{{A|VO Side0 al mar7th 128.ogg}} '''March 7th:''' Aha! So, you're trying to learn how to reject Herta, and then put it into practice!
::{{A|VO Side0 al arlan 129.ogg}} '''Arlan:''' Yes. I found an anonymous handwritten journal while I was cleaning up &mdash; it mentioned 36 different strategies for relieving pressure. That's where I read about the trials.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Of the heart, of the mirror, of the self...?
::{{A|VO Side0 al arlan 130.ogg}} '''Arlan:''' Yes. There were detailed notes, so... I wanted to give them a try.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Those trials really made Asta worry.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Don't just read any anonymous journal!
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Did you really think it would help...?
::{{A|VO Side0 al arlan 131.ogg}} '''Arlan:''' I'm sorry, my lady... I didn't want to bother anyone, so I didn't mention it.
::{{A|VO Side0 al asta 218.ogg}} '''Asta:''' So... you don't feel pressured around me?
::{{A|VO Side0 al arlan 132.ogg}} '''Arlan:''' I've never felt pressured around you, my lady.
::{{A|VO Side0 al mar7th 129.ogg}} '''March 7th:''' Alright, alright &mdash; it's all a misunderstanding. You two should reflect on your actions!
::{{A|VO Side0 al mar7th 130 m.ogg}} {{A|VO Side0 al mar7th 130 f.ogg}} '''March 7th:''' Right, (Trailblazer)?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} You need to talk to each other more.
:::{{A|VO Side0 al mar7th 131.ogg}} '''March 7th:''' Yeah! See, the two of us would never have misunderstandings like this.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} You both need to start saying what you're thinking.
:::{{A|VO Side0 al mar7th 132.ogg}} '''March 7th:''' Yup! I always say what I'm thinking.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} You both need to use your brains more.
:::{{A|VO Side0 al mar7th 133.ogg}} '''March 7th:''' That's righ&mdash; Hey! This is supposed to be a happy moment!
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Anyways, Dan Heng was right...
::{{A|VO Side0 al mar7th 134.ogg}} '''March 7th:''' You keep saying that &mdash; what did Dan Heng even say...
::{{A|VO Side0 al arlan 133.ogg}} '''Arlan:''' ...Thank you for helping Lady Asta... and for coming to find me.
::{{A|VO Side0 al mar7th 135.ogg}} '''March 7th:''' You're welcome! Although if you really wanna thank me... let me play holodisc with Peppy &mdash; pleaaaase~?
